title: Oat Sourdough Rolls
ingredients: ['225ml sourdough starter', '120ml warm water', '3 tablespoons honey', '1 tablespoon treacle', '1 egg, lightly beaten', '110g margarine', '40g rolled oats', '375g plain flour', '1 teaspoon salt', '1/2 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '2 teaspoons dried active baking yeast']
